module TopModule (
    input logic a,
    input logic b,
    input logic c,
    input logic d,
    output logic out_sop,
    output logic out_pos
);

assign out_sop = (a & ~b & c & d) | (~a & b & c & d) | (~a & ~b & ~c & ~d); // 2, 7, 15
assign out_pos = (~(a | b) & ~(a & ~c & ~d) & ~(b & ~c & d)); // 0, 1, 4, 5, 6, 9, 10, 13, 14

endmodule
